{
  "texts": [
    "As one of the participants mentioned, I come across a lot of content every day since I use Facebook always.",
    "Whenever I come across a commercial advertisement, I really don't find any reason why it is there.",
    "I neither like this product nor do I need it now.",
    "On the other hand, sometimes, I do see a product while scrolling through Facebook, but I really do not understand where it comes from!",
    "Is Facebook using my information from all the places, or what?"
  ]
}